{"type":"section","nativeType":"section","number":"3306","heading":"Remedies of the United States","label":"3306 Remedies of the United States","identifier":"/us/usc/t28/s3306","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t28/ptVI/ch176/schD","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft28%2Fs3306","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":["Editorial Notes","References in TextThe Federal Rules of Civil Procedure, referred to in subsec. (a), are set out in the Appendix to this title.","Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","Effective DateSection effective 180 days after , and applicable with respect to certain actions for debts owed the United States pending in court on that effective date, see , set out as a note under .Nov. 29, 1990section 3631 of Pub. L. 101–647section 3001 of this title"],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"a","heading":".—In General","label":"a .—In General","identifier":"/us/usc/t28/s3306/a","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t28/s3306","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft28%2Fs3306%2Fa","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t28/s3306/a/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t28/s3306/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft28%2Fs3306%2Fa%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"avoidance of the transfer or obligation to the extent necessary to satisfy the debt to the United States;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t28/s3306/a/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t28/s3306/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft28%2Fs3306%2Fa%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"a remedy under this chapter against the asset transferred or other property of the transferee; or","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"3","heading":null,"label":"3","identifier":"/us/usc/t28/s3306/a/3","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t28/s3306/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft28%2Fs3306%2Fa%2F3","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"any other relief the circumstances may require.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"b","heading":".—Limitation","label":"b .—Limitation","identifier":"/us/usc/t28/s3306/b","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t28/s3306","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft28%2Fs3306%2Fb","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t28/s3306/b/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t28/s3306/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft28%2Fs3306%2Fb%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"under section 3304(b)(1)(A) within 6 years after the transfer was made or the obligation was incurred or, if later, within 2 years after the transfer or obligation was or could reasonably have been discovered by the claimant;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t28/s3306/b/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t28/s3306/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft28%2Fs3306%2Fb%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"under subsection (a)(1) or (b)(1)(B) of section 3304 within 6 years after the transfer was made or the obligation was incurred; or","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"3","heading":null,"label":"3","identifier":"/us/usc/t28/s3306/b/3","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t28/s3306/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft28%2Fs3306%2Fb%2F3","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"under section 3304(a)(2) within 2 years after the transfer was made or the obligation was incurred.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}]}
